    "Consequently, conventional statistical measurements that assume normality, such as the analysis of variance (ANOVA) test, did not apply to this dataset.",
    "Given these observations, we determined that nonparametric testing was the appropriate statistical method for our analysis.",
    "We utilised the Mann-Whitney U test, a recommended non-parametric test for comparing two unrelated samples when the data are not normally distributed (Field, 2013).",
    "Therefore, the interpretation of our results was approached with due consideration of these analytical choices and the inherent attributes of the collected data.",
    "The key performance indicator examined in this section is the reaction time required by the participants to activate/deactivate ADAS functions correctly."
